ALSO OFF THE NORTHWEST COAST OF AUSTRALIA, CHEVRON HOLDS

SIGNIFICANT EQUITY INTERESTS IN THE LARGE NATURAL-GAS RESOURCE

OF THE GREATER GORGON AREA. THE COMPANY INITIALLY HELD A

