VARIABLE-ROYALTY AGREEMENTS, NET

OIL-EQUIVALENT PRODUCTION INCREASED 4 PERCENT IN 2009 AND 3

PERCENT IN 2008, WHEN COMPARED WITH PRIOR YEARS PRODUCTION.

