PRODUCTION ACTIVITIES. THE ESTIMATES OF CRUDE-OIL AND NATURAL-GAS RESERVES ARE IMPORTANT TO THE

TIMING OF EXPENSE RECOGNITION FOR COSTS INCURRED.

