SHARES ACQUIRED IN EXCHANGE FOR A U.S. UPSTREAM PROPERTY AND $280 IN CASH. THE CARRYING VALUE OF

THIS PROPERTY IN PROPERTIES, PLANT AND EQUIPMENT ON THE CONSOLIDATED BALANCE SHEET WAS NOT

